eecalcs.conductors

Class Conductor

  • java.lang.Object
    • eecalcs.conductors.Conductor
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Circuit

    public class Conductor
extends java.lang.Object
    Encapsulates the properties and methods for a single conductor as a physical real life object.

      • isCopperCoated

        public boolean isCopperCoated()
        Indicates if this copper conductor is coated. Notice that this property has no meaning when this conductor metal is aluminum.
        Returns:
        True if coated, false otherwise

      • setCopperCoated
